Like the above commands, but use Latin-1 encoding.
@kindex C-c C-e u
@kindex C-c C-e U
@item C-c C-e u @ @ @r{and} @ @ C-c C-e U
Like the above commands, but use UTF-8 encoding.
@kindex C-c C-e v a
@kindex C-c C-e v n
